                     <interp inst="t18271206-240-person1291" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was sitting at tea - I heard the cry Stop thief! I ran out, and picked up one pair of stockings four or five doors off - I gave them to Mr. Slater - I did not see the prisoner near the house.</p>
               <p>
            
